      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONJOIN (1) finished out of the frame in fourth when well in the market over the mile at this track two-and-a-half weeks ago. Suitably placed dropping back to a sprinting trip so anticipating a big run this time. FIRST FEELING (5) hit the frame two starts ago at this track but ran below par last time. Likely improver with strong prospects. FIREFINCH (4) resumes. Didn't make an impact at her only run last prep on December 14 but has good early toe so she should be handy in the run. One of the main contenders. INITIALLY (2) didn't fire a shot on debut last start over 1100m at Gawler. Will take a lot from that experience. Anticipating a better performance. CAPPA GRANDE (3) returns and looks best of the rest.",
